document_data.History:
The barony was founded in the {{YearlinkName|133}} by Artor Morlin some time after he fled from the [[Shoon Imperium]].

It came to an end in the {{YearlinkName|403}}, but left a legacy of fear and tales of horrific monstrosities that dwelled within the ruins of the barony's castle. The Baron of Blood fled for the settlement that later came to be known as [[Waterdeep]] and formed a lair within the [[Dungeon of the Crypt]].

A remnant of Morlin Castle could be accessed via the [[Ethereal Plane]]. It was used by Artor Morlin as an emergency redoubt.{{Cite_dungeon/128/Vampires_of_Waterdeep:_The_Fireplace_Level|83}}
